flowRoot.flowPara: A hacker, to me, is someone who does what they do because they love it. You know, whether or not it makes them money they're doing it because they love it; they're really into it. Whatever they're enthusiastic about they learn as much as they can and then they improve upon it and then they share it with the world. That's what a hacker is to me.
Every Wednesday from 8pm at Guppy's Enterprise Club on Nunnery Lane
York Hackspace is a place for anyone who is or wants to be a hacker.
All hackers, tinkerers and makers welcome to join.
If you're interested in coming to the next meeting, please let us know via the mailing list, at least 3 hours before the meeting.
